Change the title color by adding color: yellow; inside the curly braces
Change the font by adding font-family: &lsquo;Roboto Mono&rsquo;, monospace; inside the curly braces and adding @import url(&lsquo;https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Mono'); at the top of the CSS tab
